<p>Reports incorrect values of <code>max</code> and <code>min</code> values in Bean Validation constraint annotations.</p>

<p><strong>Example:</strong></p>
<pre><code>
public class Car {
  @NotNull
  @Size(min = 14, max = <strong>2</strong>) // 'max' value is less than 'min' value
  private String licensePlate;
}
</code></pre>
